data.description: BUYER FINANCE FELL THROUGH - Already appraised, this stunning 3 unit multi-family property located in the heart of Detroit, near the revitalized Gratiot Corridor and minutes to downtown and Wayne State University is back on the market. This property features 3 unique units, each with its own character and charm. The main floor unit boasts 2 spacious bedrooms, perfect for a small family or roommates. The second floor unit is the largest unit on the property, with 4 bedrooms ideal for multiple tenants. The top floor unit is a cozy studio, perfect for a student or young professional.  This property has undergone a complete interior renovation, with all new drywall, interior paint, a new roof, a new back deck, new light fixtures, new bathrooms and new siding on the rear of the home. New owners can make a decision on exterior finishes. Additionally, with an acceptable offer, all furnishings will be included, making this property an even more valuable investment.  Whether you're looking to add a lucrative investment property to your portfolio or searching for a place to call home, this multi-family property is sure to impress. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a piece of Detroit's historic charm. Schedule your private showing today! Professional pictures coming soon of main level. Pics included are second level and third level units.
